# Project Background

This project is a CLI tool.

Its dedicated mission is to help AI coding projects continuously improve:

- observability
- code quality
- delivery efficiency evolution

# Core Positioning

The CLI should be treated as an engineering copilot for AI coding workflows.

It focuses on making the development process measurable, governable, and continuously optimizable.

# Expected Outcome

Every new feature or change should align with this project background:

- strengthen observability signals and diagnostics
- improve code quality confidence and maintainability
- reduce friction and increase engineering execution efficiency
